<asp:Content ID="Content4" ContentPlaceHolderID="ContentPlaceHolder4" Runat="Server">

The Red War is the main story campaign at the launch of Destiny 2. Here are the 17 story missions of The Red War:<br /><br />
<br />
Homecoming - Return to The City and protect your fellow Guardians from an assault from a new legion of The Cabal.<br /><br />
Exodus - Escape the ruins of The City and make your way to The Farm.<br /><br />
Spark - While Hathorne offers shelter to those who fled the City, a vision points to a long-forgotten place.<br /><br />
Devrim Kay - Hawthrone has asked you to help her friend Devrim. Find him in the ruind town of Trostland.<br /><br />
Hope - Commander Zavala is building a resistance at a moon of Saturn. Make contact and join the fight.<br /><br />
Riptide - Without power, Zavala's resistance has hit a wall. Travel deeper into the Arcology and help them past it.<br /><br />
Utopia - Venture deep into the heart of the Hive to retrieve a powerful Golden Age CPU—and make it out alive.<br /><br />
Looped - No one's heard from Cayde-6 since the Hunter took off for an uncharted world. Track him down.<br /><br />
Six - A crashed colony ship, an interspecies war... Cayde-6 got that adventure he wanted. Go save him from it.<br /><br />
Sacrilege - Since the loss of her Light, Ikora has many questions and she's not leaving Io without answers.<br /><br />
Fury - Help Ikora use the Warmind on Io to learn more about the Almighty and turn the tide of the war.<br /><br />
Payback - Payback begins in The Gulch, part of the European Dead Zone.<br /><br />
Unbroken - This mission begins aboard the carrier you grounded in the previous mission.<br /><br />
Larceny - With Thumos’s key codes in-hand, it’s time to take his ship out for a joyride.<br /><br />
1AU - In this mission, you’ll be taking the fight to the Red Legion.<br /><br />
Chosen - Save them all.



